    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Finely slice your <strong>parsnip[s]</strong> into discs</p><p>Finely slice your <strong>potato[es]</strong> into discs</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/parsnip-and-goats-cheese-tart-with-root-veg-crisps-and-salad/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>potato discs</strong> and <strong>parsnip discs </strong>to a large heat-proof bowl covered with <strong>cling film </strong>and pierce a few holes in the top</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave </strong>and cook for 6 min or until fork tender</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/parsnip-and-goats-cheese-tart-with-root-veg-crisps-and-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Marmite</strong>, <strong>dried thyme </strong>and your <strong>goats' cheese </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>then give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is is your <strong>Marmite & goats' cheese sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/parsnip-and-goats-cheese-tart-with-root-veg-crisps-and-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap your <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Line a baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>pastry</strong> to the tray[s] and score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife</p><p>Tip: The pastry border will puff up to give you a nice crust!</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/parsnip-and-goats-cheese-tart-with-root-veg-crisps-and-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Spread the <strong>Marmite & goats' cheese sauce</strong> over the pastry within the border</p><p>Layer <strong>most </strong>of the <strong>softened potato & parsnip discs </strong>on top with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until the pastry is until golden, cooked through and the edges have puffed up</p><p>Once done, drizzle over <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>maple syrup </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>parsnip & goats' cheese tart</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/parsnip-and-goats-cheese-tart-with-root-veg-crisps-and-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray (or two!) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>remaining softened potato & parsnip discs </strong>to the tray[s] with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until until golden and crispy \u2013 these are your <strong>root veg crisps</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/parsnip-and-goats-cheese-tart-with-root-veg-crisps-and-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to a large bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, set aside for 3-4 min to pickle</p><p>Once pickled, add your <strong>Dijon mustard</strong>, the <strong>remaining maple syrup</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Gently toss your <strong>salad </strong>and <strong>walnuts </strong>through the <strong>dressing</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>walnut & shallot salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/parsnip-and-goats-cheese-tart-with-root-veg-crisps-and-salad/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>parsnip & goats' cheese tart</strong> in half</p><p>Serve the <strong>root veg crisps </strong>and the <strong>walnut & shallot salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
